
    <h1 class="withsub cushycms"><em>Welcome</em> to a new kind of Marketplace</h1>
    <p class="subh1 cushycms">Loconomics supports local economies by matching customers with independent service providers. Bypassing large agencies and corporations means saving customers money while allowing the provider to earn more. Here at Loconomics, we think small acts add up to big changes, and we’d like to thank you for choosing a local, independent service provider.</p>

